ory/coronavirus-india-telangana-reports-first-covid-19-death-1660766-2020-03-28|title=Telangana reports first Covid-19 death|work=indiatoday.in|date=28 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| 24\n| 46\n| Female\n| {{flagdeco|India}} Indian\n| [[Gujarat]]\n|\n| Hypertension and Diabetes\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=Coronavirus patient dies in Gujarat |url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/coronavirus-patient-dies-in-gujarat/articleshow/74862694.cms?from=mdr |website=The Economic Times |accessdate=29 March 2020 |date=28 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| 25\n| 85\n| Male\n| {{flagdeco|India}} Indian\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Maharashtra]]\n|\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.deccanherald.com/national/west/mumbai-hospital-units-sealed-after-doctor-dies-of-covid-19-818717.html|title=Mumbai hospital units sealed after doctor dies of COVID-19|date=28 March 2020|work=Deccan Herald|agency=PTI|access-date=30 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|26\n|80\n|Male\n|{{Flagdeco|India}} Indian\n|\n|Hypertension and Ischemic heart disease\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://indianexpress.com/article/india/maharashtra-confirms-2-more-deaths-toll-rises-to-10-6339579/|title=Maharashtra confirms 2 more deaths, toll rises to 10|date=2020-03-31|website=The Indian Express|language=en-US|access-date=2020-03-31}}</ref>\n|-\n| 27\n| rowspan=\"4\" | March 29\n| 45\n| Male\n|{{flagdeco|India}} Indian\n|[[Gujarat]]\n|\n| Diabetes\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://english.jagran.com/india/coronavirus-outbreak-45yearold-covid19-patient-dies-in-gujarat-india-toll-rises-to22-10010137|title=Coronavirus outbreak: 45-year-old COVID-19 patient dies in Gujarat, India toll rises to 25|work=english.jagran.com|date=29 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| 28\n| 52\n| Male\n|{{flagdeco|India}} Indian\n|[[Jammu and Kashmir (union territory)|Jammu and Kashmir]]\n|\n| Liver ailment\n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/second-coronavirus-death-in-jammu-and-kashmir-52-year-old-man-dies-2202467|title=Second Coronavirus Death In 