w Delhi]]\n| Travelled from [[Yemen]]\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/a-yemen-national-is-2nd-coronavirus-casualty-in-delhi/story-qzIqICzaQnI7JkKDPEQm4N.html|title=60-year-old Yemeni national dies due to coronavirus in Delhi|date=27 March 2020|work=Hindustan Times|access-date=30 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| 22\n| rowspan=\"5\" | March 28\n| 69\n| Male\n| {{flagdeco|India}} Indian\n| [[Kerala]]\n| Travelled from [[Dubai]], [[United Arab Emirates]]\n| Blood pressure and Heart failure\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.businesstoday.in/latest/trends/coronavirus-india-cases-deaths-live-updates-lockdown-delhi-mumbai-america-italy-covid19-virus/story/399465.html|title=Coronavirus in India Live Updates: Kerala's first COVID-19 death; positive cases surge to 873|work=businesstoday.in|date=28 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| 23\n| 74\n| Male\n| {{flagdeco|India}} Indian\n| [[Telangana]]\n| Travelled to [[Delhi]]\n|\n| <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/coronavirus-india-telangana-reports-first-covid-19-death-1660766-2020-03-28|title=Telangana reports first Covid-19 death|work=indiatoday.in|date=28 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| 24\n| 46\n| Female\n| {{flagdeco|India}} Indian\n| [[Gujarat]]\n|\n| Hypertension and Diabetes\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=Coronavirus patient dies in Gujarat |url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/coronavirus-patient-dies-in-gujarat/articleshow/74862694.cms?from=mdr |website=The Economic Times |accessdate=29 March 2020 |date=28 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n| 25\n| 85\n| Male\n| {{flagdeco|India}} Indian\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Maharashtra]]\n|\n|\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.deccanherald.com/national/west/mumbai-hospital-units-sealed-after-doctor-dies-of-covid-19-818717.html|title=Mumbai hospital units sealed after doctor dies of COVID-19|date=28 March 2020|work=Deccan Herald|agency=PTI|access-date=30 March 2020}}</ref>\n|-\n|26\n|80\n|Male\n|{{Flagdeco|India}} Indian\n|\n|Hypertensio